OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782173903
OL,3,CIncrease in teenage psychosis cases
OL,4,Clinked to vapes laced with spice
OL,6,FPsychiatrist Dr Hilary Reed warns that
OL,7,Fin the last two years, the number of
OL,8,Fpeople she's treating with psychosis
OL,9,Fhas increased from one or two a year
OL,10,Fto 10, Good Morning Britain
OL,11,FCorrespondent Amelia Beckett reports
OL,13,FAn NHS psychiatrist has told Good
OL,14,FMorning Britain a huge increase in
OL,15,Fteenage psychosis cases is likely to
OL,16,Fbe linked to vapes laced with the
OL,17,F'zombie drug' spice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
