PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782173903
OL,3,CIncrease in teenage psychosis cases
OL,4,Clinked to vapes laced with spice
OL,6,FDr Hilary Reed works in the north of
OL,7,FEngland and usually treats one or two
OL,8,Fcases of psychosis a year but in 2025
OL,9,Fthat jumped to 10 cases.
OL,11,F"It does appear that there's an
OL,12,Fassociation between vapes containing
OL,13,Fspice and psychotic illness", she said
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
