OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782173903
OL,3,CIncrease in teenage psychosis cases
OL,4,Clinked to vapes laced with spice
OL,6,F"We can't definitely say this is
OL,7,Fcausative but the evidence does
OL,8,Fsuggest these vapes are a huge issue
OL,9,Fthat definitely needs more research
OL,10,Fbecause my concern here is are we
OL,11,Fseeing the beginning of what could be
OL,12,Fa nationwide increase in psychosis
OL,13,Famong young people."
OL,15,FSpice is a synthetic drug designed to
OL,16,Fmimic the effects of cannabis. However
OL,17,Fthese unregulated, highly potent
OL,18,Fchemicals are extremely dangerous,
OL,19,Funpredictable, and very addictive.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]
