OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782173903
OL,3,CIncrease in teenage psychosis cases
OL,4,Clinked to vapes laced with spice
OL,6,FThey are now making their way into
OL,7,Fvapes products sold to teenagers
OL,8,Fbadged as containing cannabis, where
OL,9,Fin many cases drug dealers actually
OL,10,Fuse spice because it is much cheaper.
OL,12,FResearch from the University of Bath
OL,13,Ffound that up to one in four vapes
OL,14,Fconfiscated from schools now contain
OL,15,Fthe drug.
OL,17,FAt Wales High School in Rotherham the
OL,18,Fheadteacher has resorted to installing
OL,19,Fvape sensors in a number of toilets to
OL,20,Ftry and crack down on the issue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
