PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782173903
OL,3,CIncrease in teenage psychosis cases
OL,4,Clinked to vapes laced with spice
OL,6,F"In the last couple of years we've
OL,7,Fseen vaping take off so much,
OL,8,Fcigarettes are no longer an issue and
OL,9,Fwe had to keep up," Lisa McCall said.
OL,11,F"These teenagers can buy them so
OL,12,Feasily and many try to vape on school
OL,13,Fpremises."
