CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782173903
OL,3,CIncrease in teenage psychosis cases
OL,4,Clinked to vapes laced with spice
OL,6,FWe have had cases with students giving
OL,7,Feach other vapes where they don't know
OL,8,Fwhat is in them but we suspect it has
OL,9,Fbeen spice.
OL,11,F"In one particular case a student had
OL,12,Fto go to hospital and we had to
OL,13,Fpermanently exclude a number of pupils
OL,14,Fwhich is a step we don't usually take
OL,15,Fbut this is such a serious issue."
OL,17,FA government spokesperson said: "These
OL,18,Fvapes are illegal. Selling them can
OL,19,Fget you up to 14 years in prison.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@bO]yD@aOU
