OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782173903
OL,3,CIncrease in teenage psychosis cases
OL,4,Clinked to vapes laced with spice
OL,6,F"That's why we continue to work with
OL,7,Fenforcement agencies like Trading
OL,8,FStandards to crack down on illegal and
OL,9,Funderage sale of tobacco and vapes,
OL,10,Fbacked by #30 million in funding."
OL,12,F"To make sure every young person gets
OL,13,Fthe support they need, we're investing
OL,14,Fa record #16.1 billion in NHS mental
OL,15,Fhealth services.
OL,17,F"We are expanding support in schools
OL,18,Fand colleges, focusing on earlier
OL,19,Fintervention and better access."
